Package soot.toDex

Class ExprVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.toDex.ExprVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExprSwitch, Switch
    public class ExprVisitor
extends Object
implements ExprSwitch
    A visitor that builds a list of instructions from the Jimple expressions it visits.

    Use Switchable#apply(soot.util.Switch) with this visitor to add statements. These are added to the instructions in the StmtVisitor.
    If the expression is part of an assignment or an if statement, use setDestinationReg(Register) and setTargetForOffset(Stmt), respectively.
    See Also:
    StmtVisitor
